Aloha President Kouchi, Speaker Nakamura, and Members of the Legislature:
This is to inform you that on June 3, 2026, the following bill was signed into law;
H.B. NO. 1823, H.D. 2, S.D. 2, RELATING TO THE COASTAL ZONE
C.D. 2 MANAGEMENT ACT.
